&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp [H]- C'était bien le moment <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp You gasp at an enraged shadow beast in astonishment<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp ...<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp * Le susdit prend la fuite, relativement peu satisfait de l'accueil... *<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp ...<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp [T]- ADD a shadow beast cook<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp [H]- 3<br>
